Name:                bnfc-cabal
Version:             0.1
Synopsis:            Installation tool for your own labelled bnf
Description:         cabalBnfc uses bnfc to build haskell modules
                     for a given labelled grammar. The modules can
                     now be easily installed using cabal.
License:             GPL
Author:              Pascal Hof
Maintainer:          Pascal Hof
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.6
Build-Type:          Simple
Executable bnfcCabal
  Hs-Source-Dirs:      src
  Build-Depends:       base < 5,
                       BNFC >= 2.7.1,
                       filepath >= 1.1.0.2,
                       directory >= 1.0.0.3,
                       process >= 1.0.1.1,
                       Cabal >= 1.22.0.0 ,
                       mtl

  GHC-Options:         -Wall
  Main-Is:             Bnfc-cabal.hs
